    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A mid-1940s precursor of Abstract Expressionism that itself was a transitional synthesis of various forms of abstraction with Surrealist automatism.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
